                                    <title type="incomplete">Lectionary</title>
                                    <note>The fragment was not finished.</note>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ዘለዓለም፡ ሥላሴ፡
                                        ንጹሕ፡ ወንጡፍ፡
                                        ወጽሩይ፡ ወሥሙር፡ በኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር። መልእክተ፡ ጳውሎስ፡ <sic>ለሰበ፡</sic>
                                        ተ<supplied reason="omitted">ሰ</supplied>ሎንቄ፡ በረከቱ፡ ይኩን፡ ምስለ፡
                                        ፍቁሩ፡
                                        <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14888Mikael">ሚካኤል፡</persName></incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.2">
